{
 "prompt": "Elegant Korean woman, 40s, luminous skin, chic silk blouse, serene expression, Opulent minimalist spa suite, soft diffused sunlight, flowing sheer fabrics, ELS, soft focus, morning glow, looking towards a table where the product will soon appear, Rembrandt lighting, Phase One IQ4, 8k, hyper-realistic --no text, logo",
 "styling": { "style": "dreamy", "color": "warm gold, soft ivory", "lighting": "Rembrandt" }
